                                            <br>
                                                                Previously attributed to <a href=https://www.harvardartmuseums.org/collections/person/21349>Agnolo Gaddi</a>, Italian                                                                                                                                                                      (1350 - 1396)
                                            <br>
                                                                Previously attributed to <a href=https://www.harvardartmuseums.org/collections/person/21969>Niccolò di Pietro Gerini</a>, Italian                                                                                                                                                                      (1368 - 1415)
                                            <br>
                                    </dd>
            
