                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Burton B. Fredericksen and Federico Zeri, <em>Census of Pre-Nineteenth-Century Italian Paintings in North American Public Collections</em>, Harvard University Press (Cambridge, MA, 1972), p. 81 [as by Niccolò di Pietro Gerini]
                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Miklós Boskovits, <em>Pittura Fiorentina all vigilia del Rinascimento, 1370-1400</em>, Editrice Edam (Florence, 1975), p. 376, repr. as fig. 223
                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Howard Mayer Brown, Catalogus: A Corpus of Trecento Pictures with Musical Subject Matter, <em>Imago Musicae</em>, Bärenreiter-Verlag (Basel, 1985), Part I, Installment 2, pp. 276-277, cat. no. 344, repr. p. 277
